      ],
      "message": "contrib: Retry signet mining after grind failure\n\nbitcoin-util grind can exhaust the nonce search space on higher difficulty signet chains. Retry with a fresh block header by incrementing the block time when the grinder reports that it could not satisfy the target.\n\nAdd functional test coverage for the retry path by wrapping the grinder so the first attempt fails and the second attempt delegates to bitcoin-util grind.\n\nFixes #30102.",
